50|$|The Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers, {{based in}} Piscataway, New Jersey, USA, {{promotes}} the creation, development {{and application of}} electrical and information technologies and sciences, {{for the benefit of}} humanity and the profession. Its <b>Broadcast</b> <b>Technology</b> Society is specifically involved with devices, equipment, techniques and systems related to <b>broadcast</b> <b>technology,</b> including the production, distribution, transmission and propagation aspects.|$|E
